# SEO Rules (Landing Page)

## Metadata
- Use Next.js Metadata API in `app/layout.tsx`.
- Set:
  - title (template + default)
  - description
  - openGraph
  - twitter card
  - icons
- Add canonical URL once domain is known.

## Crawlability
- Implement:
  - `app/robots.ts`
  - `app/sitemap.ts`

## Content SEO
- Exactly one H1 on the landing page.
- Use descriptive headings (H2/H3) for sections.
- Include descriptive copy (not just CTA text).

## Structured data
- Add JSON-LD (Organization + Website). Keep it minimal and accurate.
